<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">In this section, the text of <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s19jj/a">16 U.S.C. 19jj(a)</ref> is omitted as unnecessary. The text of <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s19jj/e">16 U.S.C. 19jj(e)</ref> is omitted because the term “regimen” is not used in the revised title. The text of <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s19jj/g">16 U.S.C. 19jj(g)</ref> is omitted because a marine or aquatic park system resource is a kind of park system resource.</p>
